Mahindra Could Build a Pick-Up Truck in South Africa, Business Report Says

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-03-08T05:21:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-08/mahindra-could-build-a-pick-up-truck-in-south-africa-business-report-says.html
  Mahindra & Mahindra Ltd. (MM)  may start
production of a pick-up truck in  South Africa  by the end of this
year or early 2012, Business Report said, citing Ashok Thakur,
the chief executive officer of Mahindra South Africa.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
